nces crackdown on 10,000 foreign students]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131101756.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/3-things-opt-employers-should-check-as-ice-announces-crackdown-on-10000-foreign-students/articleshow/131101756.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/3-things-opt-employers-should-check-as-ice-announces-crackdown-on-10000-foreign-students/articleshow/131101756.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-15T00:19:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131101799,imgsize-181406.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Mahatma Gandhi: “In prayer it is better to have a heart without words than words without a heart.”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131101219.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-mahatma-gandhi-in-prayer-it-is-better-to-have-a-heart-without-words-than-words-without-a-heart-/articleshow/131101219.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-mahatma-gandhi-in-prayer-it-is-better-to-have-a-heart-without-words-than-words-without-a-heart-/articleshow/131101219.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-15T00:00:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131101411,imgsize-101356.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['An aggressor': Iran tells UAE to ‘accept responsibility’ as tensions flare at Brics meeting in New Delhi]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131099744.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran accused the UAE of direct military involvement in attacks against Tehran during a BRICS meeting, escalating tensions. Tehran claims Abu Dhabi facilitated aggression and warned of retaliation against facilities aiding US or Israeli operations. This dispute complicates efforts to finalize a joint BRICS communique.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/an-aggressor-iran-tells-uae-to-accept-responsibility-as-tensions-flare-at-brics-meeting-in-new-delhi/articleshow/131099744.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/an-aggressor-iran-tells-uae-to-accept-responsibility-as-tensions-flare-at-brics-meeting-in-new-delhi/articleshow/131099744.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T23:19:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131100422,imgsize-1022777.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Walter Benjamin: “In the end, we get older, we kill everyone who loves us through the worries we give them, through the troubled tenderness we inspire in them, and the fears we ceaselessly cause.”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131099755.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-walter-benjamin-in-the-end-we-get-older-we-kill-everyone-who-loves-us-through-the-worries-we-give-them-through-the-troubled-tenderness-we-inspire-in-them-and-the-fears-we-ceaselessly-cause-/articleshow/131099755.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-walter-benjamin-in-the-end-we-get-older-we-kill-everyone-who-loves-us-through-the-worries-we-give-them-through-the-troubled-tenderness-we-inspire-in-them-and-the-fears-we-ceaselessly-cause-/articleshow/131099755.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T23:12:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131100164,imgsize-15598.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Latvian PM resigns due to split in alliance over Russian drones]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131099848.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Latvian Prime Minister Evika Silina resigned after her coalition government collapsed due to disagreements over Ukrainian drone incidents. The Progressive Party withdrew support after Silina dismissed the defense minister for failing to address drones flying from Russia. President Edgars Rinkevics will now consult parties to form a new government ahead of October elections.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/latvian-pm-resigns-due-to-split-in-alliance-over-russian-drones/articleshow/131099848.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/latvian-pm-resigns-due-to-split-in-alliance-over-russian-drones/articleshow/131099848.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T23:06:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131099964,imgsize-18454.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kick streamer Clavicular’s jaw hammering confession takes unexpected turn after revealing life with multiple girlfriends]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131099846.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Internet personality Clavicular went viral after admitting he used a hammer on his jaw as a teenager to improve his appearance. He said his parents even hid hammers to stop him. The interview also focused on his current dating life, where he claimed to be seeing multiple women at the same time. The clip quickly spread online and sparked heavy discussion.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-claviculars-jaw-hammering-confession-takes-unexpected-turn-after-revealing-life-with-multiple-girlfriends/articleshow/131099846.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-claviculars-jaw-hammering-confession-takes-unexpected-turn-after-revealing-life-with-multiple-girlfriends/articleshow/131099846.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T23:00:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131099835,imgsize-84454.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin former CEO sentenced to 5 years in prison over $212 million fraud in New Jersey, asked to pay $125 million]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131098972.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-origin-former-ceo-sentenced-to-5-years-in-prison-over-212-million-fraud-in-new-jersey-asked-to-pay-125-million/articleshow/131098972.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-origin-former-ceo-sentenced-to-5-years-in-prison-over-212-million-fraud-in-new-jersey-asked-to-pay-125-million/articleshow/131098972.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T22:35:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="htt